citations:
    citation-acok-prologue:
        source: source-acok
        properties:
            locator: "Prologue"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Prologue POV: Maester Cressen at Dragonstone. Opens with the red comet over Dragonstone at dawn. Introduces Cressen, Pylos, Shireen, Patchface. Stannis and Melisandre discussed. Cressen attempts to poison Melisandre at the feast; the poison kills Cressen but Melisandre survives unharmed. First appearance of Davos in the chapter, returning from his failed mission to win storm lords to Stannis's cause."
